  "text": "All the physical mixtures were prepared by manually mixing the proper components in a mortar, and their compositions are reported in Table 1 . Physical mixture A was prepared with a molar ratio between KP and Me CD equal to 1 : 1 as was suggested by a previous work where KP/Me CD complexes were prepared through conventional techniques [CITATION_1] . Mixtures B and C were prepared introducing a 15% excess and a 15% defect of KP with respect to the equimolar content of mixture A.",
